title: Day-Lee Foods Inc. Recalls Frozen Ready-To-Eat Poultry Products Due to Misbranding and Undeclared Allergens
summary: EDITOR'S NOTE: August 8, 2023 – This recall release is being updated to provide a new media contact. Members of the media with questions about the recall can contact Kotaro Fujita, General Manager, Day-Lee Foods, Inc., at (562) 802-6872. WASHINGTON, Aug. 5, 2023 – Day-Lee...
